.TH "BEEHIIV-SUBSCRIPTION-TAGS-CREATE" "1" "Apr 2026" "beehiiv-cli" "Beehiiv CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
beehiiv-subscription-tags-create - Add subscription tag


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbeehiiv subscription-tags create  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Add subscription tag

.PP
Adds tags to a subscription. If the tag does not exist on the publication, it will be created automatically.

.PP
API path: /publications/{publicationId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/tags


